snippet: DeAndre Jordan had 15 points and 13 rebounds, Chris Paul added 13 points and 14 assists and the Los Angeles Clippers cruised to a 114-90 victory over the Boston Celtics on Monday night....
lead_paragraph: DeAndre Jordan had 15 points and 13 rebounds, Chris Paul added 13 points and 14 assists and the Los Angeles Clippers cruised to a 114-90 victory over the Boston Celtics on Monday night.

headline.main: Paul, Jordan Lead Clippers Past Celtics, 114-90
headline.print_headline: Paul, Jordan Lead Clippers Past Celtics, 114-90
